body.description: KEY FEATURES: Processor Powerful TV processing See lifelike picture quality in incredible 4K resolution. The powerful 4K Processor X1 enhances the picture to deliver scenes full of rich colors and sharp details. Everything you watch is upscaled close to 4K quality with smooth and clear motion. Color & Contrast Beautiful 4K HDR picture See your favorite content burst to life on screen with High Dynamic Range (HDR) contrast. Every scene is enhanced to make colors and shadows even more natural and precise, so picture quality is closer than every to real life. Google TV The entertainment you love. With help from Google. With 700,000+ movies and TV episodes, live TV, and more available across 10,000+ apps, Google TV takes streaming and live TV to the next level — bringing together your favorite entertainment from across your apps and organizing it all, just for you. Searching is easy – just ask Google. Press the Google Assistant button on your remote and try saying “find action movies” to search across your favorite apps.1 Features for PS5 Exclusive features for PlayStation 5 Get detailed, responsive game play and feel the action all around you with Sony TV exclusive feature for the PlayStation 5 console. Auto HDR Tone Mapping automatically adjusts the HDR settings of the PS5 console to the TV for detailed, high-contrast scenes, and Auto Genre Picture Mode automatically adjusts the picture quality during gaming or streaming.2 Motion Smooth and clear, even in fast scenes TV that keeps up with real life. Motionflow XR refresh rate technology keeps movement smooth and clear, allowing fast moving action sequences in sports and movies to be seen with lifelike clarity.
